These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
House: colonial, tower, farmhouse, art-deco, modern, wooden, townhouse
The people have 7 different hobbies: writing, photography, filmmaking, board-games, woodworking, drawing, singing
 1. the art-deco house is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the art-deco house##1
 3. the townhouse house is on the right of the wooden house##1
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 5. the farmhouse house is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
 7. the modern house is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 8. the colonial house is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
11. the townhouse house is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| House           | modern | art-deco | tower | farmhouse | colonial | wooden | townhouse |
| Hobby   | writing    | woodworking   | board-games      | drawing | filmmaking    | photography    | singing         |

