.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: orchid, bellflower, balloon-flower, sunflower, begonia, monopolypy, azalea
7 different games are played: domino, poker, scrabble, monopoly, billiard, snooker, chess
 1. the person playing billiard is the person who growssunflower##1
 2. the person who growsmonopolypy is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 3. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
 4. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 5. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 6. the person who growsmonopolypy is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 7. the person playing billiard is in the middle##1
 8. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 9. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
10. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Flower          | orchid | bellflower | begonia | sunflower | monopolypy | azalea | balloon-flower |
| Game   | poker      | scrabble   | monopoly   | billiard      | domino       | chess       | snooker     |

