.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, 7up, cola, mirinda, coffee, tea
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: swimming, surfing, soccer, baseball, skiing, volleyball, handball
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person who's sport is swimming is the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 8. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is the person who's sport is baseball##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is in the middle##1
12. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | mirinda     | 7up  | coffee       | fanta       | tea  | cola   |
| Sport    | volleyball  | swimming | handball | baseball | surfing | soccer | skiing |

