The people's birthday is in 7 different months: february, july, march, may, november, september, august
 1. the prince-smoker is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 2. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
 5. the prince-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
 6. the chaman-smoker is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
 8. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 9. the bolivar-smoker is the person who's birthday is in november##1
10. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Cigar   | chaman    | baccarat     | havana     | bolivar      | dunhill | prince      | dannemann     |
| Birthday   | may | march | september | november | august | july | february |

