.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: rock, disco, jazz, electronic, folk, indie, funk
There 7 different types of food: apricot, banana, onion, plum, cranberry, pepper, lime
 1. the fan of disco is the person eating lime##1
 2. the person eating banana is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 3. the person eating pepper is in the middle##1
 4. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 5. the person eating cranberry is the fan of indie##1
 6. the fan of folk is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 7. the person eating pepper is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 8. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 9. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
10. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Music-Genre   | disco | jazz | indie     | electronic | funk | folk | rock |
| Food     | lime   | onion    | cranberry | pepper     | apricot         | plum     | banana        |

