 4. the craftsman house is on the left of the fan of pop##1
 5. the fan of techno is on the right of the victorian house##1
 6. the tower house is on the left of the victorian house##1
 7. the farmhouse house is the fan of trance##1
 8. the fan of house is in the middle##1
 9. the tower house is on the right of the fan of classical##1
10. the farmhouse house is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
