 4. the thai is on the right of the turkish##1
 5. the turkish is on the far left##1
 6. the german is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 8. the malaysian is in the middle##1
 9. the german is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
10. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
