.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-11::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: subway, airplane, ship, bus, van, taxi, tram
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, water, hot-chocolate, cola, lemonade, milk, tea
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 2. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person drinking water is the person driving the ship##1
 5. the person drinking cola is the person driving the van##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 9. the person drinking water is in the middle##1
10. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
11. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
12. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |   4    |     5     |    6    |   7    |
| Transport          | van | subway     | taxi | ship | airplane      | tram  | bus |
| Beverage   | cola   | lemonade | hot-chocolate  | water | soy-milk | milk | tea   |

